## Clarification Questions

1. When editing a recurring lesson's subject, does the change apply to "only this lesson" or "this and following"? Or both options?
2. Can subject be changed after the lesson is completed/cancelled, or is it locked at certain lesson statuses?
3. What happens when a Subject Master record is deleted or deactivated — are existing lessons affected?
4. For CSV import, what is the exact column name for Subject? What happens if the subject value doesn't match any Subject Master record (error or skip)?
5. For search on SF Lessons list — is this a lookup search or text search? Does it match partial subject names?
6. Cross-field validation on BO Subject Filter (AC 05.3) — which fields interact with Subject? Location? Course?
7. Is Subject displayed on the lesson list in BO, or only in the detail view?
8. When creating a lesson via "Add Lesson" on a lesson schedule, is Subject pre-filled from the schedule or left blank?
9. Does the duplicate lesson flow copy the subject to the new lesson?
10. Does Subject appear in the lesson report or only in the lesson itself?

